tagline: Awesome theme based off of the peaksea vim color scheme
body:
This is an awesome theme based off of the [peaksea color theme](http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=760) for VIM.

The initial start for this theme was the [zenburn theme](http://slinky.imukuppi.org/zenburnpage/) included with 
awesome by default. I copied all the icons and the changed the 
background to match.         

The colors are still a work in process, so don't be surprised to see 
a very zenburn-esque pallet. As always contributions are welcome!

Outside of those two credits the rest of the work thus far has been 
all mine.

--Steven Oliver
name: Peaksea-awesome
